title: Sensor Technologies: Healthcare, Wellness and Environmental Appl
description:
English | ISBN: 1430260130 | 2013 | 332 pages | PDF | 8 MB 

Sensor Technologies: Healthcare, Wellness and Environmental Applications explores the key aspects of sensor technologies, covering wired, wireless, and discrete sensors for the specific application domains of healthcare, wellness and environmental sensing. 

It discusses the social, regulatory, and design considerations specific to these domains.
